content: I'm planning to meet up with a friend from college who now lives in Chicago, and we're going to grab brunch at a trendy spot in SoHo... wait, no, I mean SoHo in NYC! We actually met up there when I was in NYC last month, and it was great to catch up. Anyway, back to Chicago - do you have any recommendations for brunch spots in Wicker Park or Bucktown?
